00:02:21.810 --> 00:02:24.360 align:middle line:84%
alter ourselves for
the sake of what

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:28.620 align:middle line:84%
gets his approval in our
childhood experience.

00:02:28.620 --> 00:02:31.470 align:middle line:84%
And without that,
there's no shame.

00:02:31.470 --> 00:02:34.360 align:middle line:84%
If anybody has-- think
by raise of hands,

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:38.460 align:middle line:84%
how maybe you've heard
of feral children?

