00:07:25.870 --> 00:07:30.190 align:middle line:90%


00:07:30.190 --> 00:07:32.380 align:middle line:90%
This is mom.

00:07:32.380 --> 00:07:33.220 align:middle line:90%
This could be dad.

00:07:33.220 --> 00:07:34.512 align:middle line:90%
