00:24:49.760 --> 00:24:52.370 align:middle line:90%


00:24:52.370 --> 00:24:55.970 align:middle line:84%
That feeling only occurs when
there's a separation internally

00:24:55.970 --> 00:24:57.682 align:middle line:90%
