00:39:45.030 --> 00:39:46.613 align:middle line:84%
So you've got a
little girl here who's

00:39:46.613 --> 00:39:49.280 align:middle line:90%
in an orphan-type situation.

00:39:49.280 --> 00:39:52.420 align:middle line:84%
