00:40:12.100 --> 00:40:13.390 align:middle line:90%
or healed, or put together.

00:40:13.390 --> 00:40:16.030 align:middle line:84%
If someone's lonely, there's no
loneliness, there's connection.

00:40:16.030 --> 00:40:17.440 align:middle line:84%
If you're in this
type of a situation,

00:40:17.440 --> 00:40:19.398 align:middle line:84%
there's no resolution
