00:40:22.220 --> 00:40:26.170 align:middle line:90%
So this is when we have to cope.

00:40:26.170 --> 00:40:28.722 align:middle line:84%
Coping, even though it saves
your ass in the beginning,

00:40:28.722 --> 00:40:30.430 align:middle line:84%
always leads to problems
in the long-run.

00:40:30.430 --> 00:40:33.110 align:middle line:90%


00:40:33.110 --> 00:40:37.360 align:middle line:84%
So in this circumstance,
how is she going to cope?

00:40:37.360 --> 00:40:38.830 align:middle line:10%
Knowing that coping
is all about,

00:40:38.830 --> 00:40:41.950 align:middle line:10%
how do I keep myself safe
and feeling the best possible

00:40:41.950 --> 00:40:45.578 align:middle line:10%
in the scenario that I
can't change anything?

00:40:45.578 --> 00:40:46.620 align:middle line:90%
You just saw it on stage.

