What's the answer?

00:40:47.420 --> 00:40:49.172 align:middle line:90%
>> I don't need it.

00:40:49.172 --> 00:40:50.158 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:40:50.158 --> 00:40:53.120 align:middle line:90%


00:40:53.120 --> 00:40:59.010 align:middle line:84%
So she's going to split into
a part that does not need it

00:40:59.010 --> 00:41:03.720 align:middle line:84%
