which really needs it.

00:41:03.720 --> 00:41:08.620 align:middle line:84%
Because this is the one that
kept her safe her whole life,

00:41:08.620 --> 00:41:10.590 align:middle line:84%
this is one she's
going to identify with.

00:41:10.590 --> 00:41:13.120 align:middle line:90%


00:41:13.120 --> 00:41:15.540 align:middle line:84%
Now there's this connection
that happens here.

00:41:15.540 --> 00:41:18.420 align:middle line:84%
Because this is the one
that keeps you safe,

00:41:18.420 --> 00:41:19.920 align:middle line:84%
the connection's
here, which means

00:41:19.920 --> 00:41:21.780 align:middle line:84%
that this part of
the personality

00:41:21.780 --> 00:41:26.430 align:middle line:84%
is what's feeding through
the physical embodiment.

00:41:26.430 --> 00:41:28.188 align:middle line:84%
And so when you guys
are sitting here,

00:41:28.188 --> 00:41:29.730 align:middle line:84%
looking at this
person, like you just

00:41:29.730 --> 00:41:32.490 align:middle line:84%
were, looking at this
person from the outside,

00:41:32.490 --> 00:41:34.850 align:middle line:84%
