00:41:34.850 --> 00:41:35.650 align:middle line:90%
>> Tough.

00:41:35.650 --> 00:41:36.600 align:middle line:90%
Strong.

00:41:36.600 --> 00:41:38.850 align:middle line:84%
>> Yes, that's a tough person,
that's a strong person,

00:41:38.850 --> 00:41:39.900 align:middle line:90%
pretty scary.

00:41:39.900 --> 00:41:43.320 align:middle line:84%
Little bit scared to
cross that person.

00:41:43.320 --> 00:41:45.630 align:middle line:90%
Definitely doesn't need anyone.

00:41:45.630 --> 00:41:48.180 align:middle line:84%
You will literally describe
this person this way.

00:41:48.180 --> 00:41:49.619 align:middle line:90%
Is it the truth of them?

00:41:49.619 --> 00:41:50.597 align:middle line:90%
>> No.

00:41:50.597 --> 00:41:54.510 align:middle line:90%


00:41:54.510 --> 00:41:56.570 align:middle line:90%
>> The truth is actually both.

00:41:56.570 --> 00:41:59.400 align:middle line:84%
See, in an integrated space,
which is what's healthy for us,

00:41:59.400 --> 00:42:03.100 align:middle line:84%
we are actually the
fusion of all polarities.

00:42:03.100 --> 00:42:07.680 align:middle line:84%
So we are as independent
as we are dependent.

00:42:07.680 --> 00:42:10.350 align:middle line:84%
But when we polarize like
this so as to stay safe,

00:42:10.350 --> 00:42:13.770 align:middle line:84%
we become profoundly unstable
and profoundly unhealthy,

00:42:13.770 --> 00:42:17.795 align:middle line:84%
because we have split
ourselves in order to cope.

00:42:17.795 --> 00:42:19.170 align:middle line:84%
This gets us into
a hell of a lot

00:42:19.170 --> 00:42:21.750 align:middle line:84%
of trouble in our
day-to-day life

00:42:21.750 --> 00:42:26.670 align:middle line:84%
because she wants
a relationship.

00:42:26.670 --> 00:42:28.445 align:middle line:84%
This part is still
a part of her.

00:42:28.445 --> 00:42:30.570 align:middle line:84%
Now she's going to reject,
and deny, and disown it,

00:42:30.570 --> 00:42:34.510 align:middle line:84%
so this is going to be delegated
to the subconscious mind,

00:42:34.510 --> 00:42:36.810 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:42:36.810 --> 00:42:39.160 align:middle line:84%
You've done enough healing
that you're aware of it.

00:42:39.160 --> 00:42:41.452 align:middle line:84%
But I can't tell you how many
people I meet, especially

00:42:41.452 --> 00:42:42.330 align:middle line:90%
