00:42:55.050 --> 00:42:58.050 align:middle line:90%


00:42:58.050 --> 00:43:00.970 align:middle line:84%
If something is delegated
to the subconscious,

00:43:00.970 --> 00:43:04.150 align:middle line:84%
it's in the process
