00:43:35.272 --> 00:43:37.230 align:middle line:84%
It drives me nuts what
people teach about that.

00:43:37.230 --> 00:43:40.560 align:middle line:84%
But a better way of calling
this is the law of mirroring.

00:43:40.560 --> 00:43:42.270 align:middle line:84%
