00:56:18.177 --> 00:56:20.510 align:middle line:84%
The day comes where you hit
a wall so big that you can't

00:56:20.510 --> 00:56:21.770 align:middle line:90%
run away anymore, can you?

00:56:21.770 --> 00:56:25.790 align:middle line:84%
Doesn't matter whether
you're uncomfortable.

00:56:25.790 --> 00:56:28.460 align:middle line:84%
Then you're ready to do
the real work of healing.

00:56:28.460 --> 00:56:31.240 align:middle line:84%
So I'm hoping people can
choose that before they

00:56:31.240 --> 00:56:33.160 align:middle line:84%
get so uncomfortable
they get forced into it.

00:56:33.160 --> 00:56:36.220 align:middle line:84%
But I have never found a
way to force them into it.

00:56:36.220 --> 00:56:38.800 align:middle line:84%
Nor would I really want
to because free will

00:56:38.800 --> 00:56:40.125 align:middle line:90%
is so important.

00:56:40.125 --> 00:56:43.380 align:middle line:90%


00:56:43.380 --> 00:56:45.950 align:middle line:90%
>> I agree, but I don't see it.

00:56:45.950 --> 00:56:49.340 align:middle line:90%


00:56:49.340 --> 00:56:52.130 align:middle line:84%
Well, I mean--
meaning that I see

00:56:52.130 --> 00:56:54.470 align:middle line:84%
a lot of people who say like
you were saying earlier,

00:56:54.470 --> 00:56:57.020 align:middle line:84%
that they're loving themselves,
and they're all independent,

00:56:57.020 --> 00:56:58.160 align:middle line:84%
and they're doing
their own thing.

00:56:58.160 --> 00:56:59.690 align:middle line:84%
But they're really
not, and they're

00:56:59.690 --> 00:57:01.648 align:middle line:84%
really good at convincing
themselves and others

00:57:01.648 --> 00:57:02.568 align:middle line:90%
that they are.

00:57:02.568 --> 00:57:04.610 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, so listen for
the people that are saying

00:57:04.610 --> 00:57:06.320 align:middle line:90%
they're not there yet.

00:57:06.320 --> 00:57:07.700 align:middle line:90%
You know what I mean?

00:57:07.700 --> 00:57:10.160 align:middle line:84%
Following the teachers
who say, I am enlightened,

00:57:10.160 --> 00:57:12.820 align:middle line:90%
is a dangerous, dangerous game.

00:57:12.820 --> 00:57:14.820 align:middle line:84%
Find the ones who are
like, nope, not there yet.

00:57:14.820 --> 00:57:15.500 align:middle line:90%
They're going to be safe.

00:57:15.500 --> 00:57:17.958 align:middle line:84%
The same way as somebody who's
like, no, I'm not completely

00:57:17.958 --> 00:57:19.395 align:middle line:84%
in love with myself
yet, probably

00:57:19.395 --> 00:57:21.520 align:middle line:84%
actually is closer to
self-love than the people who

00:57:21.520 --> 00:57:24.992 align:middle line:90%
are in denial about it.

00:57:24.992 --> 00:57:27.944 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE]

