00:57:30.660 --> 00:57:31.460 align:middle line:90%
You good?

00:57:31.460 --> 00:57:32.260 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:57:32.260 --> 00:57:34.448 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:57:34.448 --> 00:57:35.444 align:middle line:90%
>> Thank you.

00:57:35.444 --> 00:57:41.920 align:middle line:90%


00:57:41.920 --> 00:57:44.210 align:middle line:84%
>> OK, so that being
said, my message today,

00:57:44.210 --> 00:57:47.450 align:middle line:84%
if you didn't get it already,
is that you have got to embrace,

00:57:47.450 --> 00:57:52.130 align:middle line:84%
that is accept, own, the parts
of yourself that people have

00:57:52.130 --> 00:57:55.190 align:middle line:84%
told you are not OK and help
other people do the same.

00:57:55.190 --> 00:57:56.690 align:middle line:84%
Because it's my
hope that we can end

00:57:56.690 --> 00:57:59.540 align:middle line:84%
the fragmentation in
ourselves and, by doing so,

00:57:59.540 --> 00:58:01.380 align:middle line:84%
end the fragmentation
in this world.

00:58:01.380 --> 00:58:04.100 align:middle line:84%
So thank you for standing
with me in this movement

00:58:04.100 --> 00:58:06.140 align:middle line:84%
and know that I love
you guys very much.

